      <memberdef kind="define" id="group__devicetree-port-endpoint_1gaf3427020d7d560c5da3df0f553988f71" prot="public" static="no">
        <name>DT_INST_PORT_BY_ID</name>
        <param><defname>inst</defname></param>
        <param><defname>pid</defname></param>
        <initializer>	<ref refid="group__sys-util_1ga358bc3e7669c860a98839a51cd526b20" kindref="member">COND_CODE_1</ref>(<ref refid="group__devicetree-generic-exist_1ga9d5cf40051d042b853f6b0088fd4500a" kindref="member">DT_NODE_EXISTS</ref>(_DT_INST_PORT_BY_ID(inst, pid)),                                \
		(_DT_INST_PORT_BY_ID(inst, pid)), (<ref refid="group__devicetree-inst_1gaaa4bfec30b277e0a8e2b0285a988d61d" kindref="member">DT_INST_CHILD</ref>(inst, port)))</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Get a port node from its id. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Given a device instance number, return a port node specified by its ID. It handles various ways of how a port could be defined.</para>
<para>Example usage with <ref refid="group__devicetree-port-endpoint_1gaf3427020d7d560c5da3df0f553988f71" kindref="member">DT_INST_PORT_BY_ID()</ref> to get the <computeroutput>port@0</computeroutput> or <computeroutput>port</computeroutput> node:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".c"><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="group__devicetree-port-endpoint_1gaf3427020d7d560c5da3df0f553988f71" kindref="member">DT_INST_PORT_BY_ID</ref>(inst,<sp/>0)</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Example devicetree fragment:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".dts"><codeline><highlight class="normal">&amp;device<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>ports<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#address-cells<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;1&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#size-cells<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;0&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>port@0<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>reg<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;0x0&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><programlisting filename=".dts"><codeline><highlight class="normal">&amp;device<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>#address-cells<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;1&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>#size-cells<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;0&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>port@0<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>reg<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;0x0&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><programlisting filename=".dts"><codeline><highlight class="normal">&amp;device<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>port<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>inst</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>instance number </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>pid</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>port ID </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>port node associated with <computeroutput>pid</computeroutput> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
