      <memberdef kind="define" id="group__devicetree-port-endpoint_1gaf1261a1a110fc0b164e6eafbaf885f7d" prot="public" static="no">
        <name>DT_NODE_REMOTE_DEVICE</name>
        <param><defname>ep</defname></param>
        <initializer>	<ref refid="group__devicetree-port-endpoint_1ga37c2b0183196f513fc2222ba5fbe30d7" kindref="member">DT_NODE_BY_ENDPOINT</ref>(<ref refid="group__devicetree-generic-id_1gab7d23294a6bf7fd44a98b48ec47d8a79" kindref="member">DT_NODELABEL</ref>(<ref refid="group__devicetree-generic-prop_1ga5995350cc7fd2d12ef7daa2487d1db54" kindref="member">DT_STRING_TOKEN</ref>(ep, remote_endpoint_label)))</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Get the remote device node from a local endpoint node. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Given an endpoint node id, return the remote device node that connects to this device via this local endpoint. This handles various ways of how a port and an endpoint could be defined as described in <ref refid="group__devicetree-port-endpoint_1gaf3427020d7d560c5da3df0f553988f71" kindref="member">DT_INST_PORT_BY_ID</ref> and <ref refid="group__devicetree-port-endpoint_1ga0d2315ddc63c986da0e90177e8d8eab8" kindref="member">DT_INST_ENDPOINT_BY_ID</ref>.</para>
<para>Example usage with <ref refid="group__devicetree-port-endpoint_1gaf1261a1a110fc0b164e6eafbaf885f7d" kindref="member">DT_NODE_REMOTE_DEVICE()</ref> to get the remote device node <computeroutput>&amp;device1</computeroutput> from the local endpoint <computeroutput>endpoint@0</computeroutput> node of the device <computeroutput>&amp;device0</computeroutput> node:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".c"><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="group__devicetree-port-endpoint_1gaf1261a1a110fc0b164e6eafbaf885f7d" kindref="member">DT_NODE_REMOTE_DEVICE</ref>(<ref refid="group__devicetree-generic-id_1gab7d23294a6bf7fd44a98b48ec47d8a79" kindref="member">DT_NODELABEL</ref>(device0_ep_out))</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Example devicetree fragment:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".dts"><codeline><highlight class="normal">&amp;device0<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>port<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#address-cells<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;1&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#size-cells<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;0&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>device0_ep_out:<sp/>endpoint@0<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>reg<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;0x0&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>remote-endpoint-label<sp/>=<sp/>&quot;device1_ep_in&quot;;</highlight></codeline>
